Class ComIncrDebut

    Command, IOriginator

    public class ComIncrDebut
extends java.lang.Object
implements Command, IOriginator
    Represents the command that increases the insertion cursor one position. Demands the engine to perform the correct operations in order to increase the position of the insert cursor in the buffer.
